soa:Encoder.name: Final Cut / Avid QuickTime
soa:Encoder.description: Creates QuickTime-wrapped files that can be used within Final Cut and Avid editing systems.

soa:Container.name: Final Cut QuickTime
soa:Container.description: The QuickTime file format for the Final cut/ Avid QuickTime encoder is a multimedia container file format that includes one or more media tracks.

soa:Parameter.name: Extension
soa:Parameter.description: The file extension used for the output.

soa:Parameter.name: Timecode
soa:Parameter.description: Determine whether to add a timecode track, and whether it should display by default.

soa:Parameter.name: Enable Fast Start
soa:Parameter.description: Select to enable fast start

soa:Parameter.name: Video Profile (--profile)
soa:Parameter.description: x.264 Video Profile

soa:Parameter.name: Video Level (--level)
soa:Parameter.description: Video Level (--level)

soa:Parameter.name: Frame Width
soa:Parameter.description: Width of the output video, in pixels.

soa:Parameter.name: Frame Height
soa:Parameter.description: Height of the output video, in pixels.

soa:Parameter.name: Frame Rate (--fps)
soa:Parameter.description: Output frame rate.

soa:Parameter.name: Interlace Mode (--no-interlaced --tff --bff)
soa:Parameter.description: Specify the interlace mode for the output material.

soa:Parameter.name: Video Bit Rate (--bitrate)
soa:Parameter.description: The video data rate.

soa:Parameter.name: Insert Closed Captions
soa:Parameter.description: Adds ATSC captions directly into the x.264 essence.

soa:Parameter.name: Use Lightspeed acceleration
soa:Parameter.description: Runs x.264 compression algorithms on Lightspeed GPUs but increases memory consumption. This only applies when the 'Lightspeed Accelerated 16-bit YCbCr 4:4:4:4' or 'Cinnafilm Tachyon' VPL is selected.

soa:Parameter.name: Use Lightspeed-accelerated preanalysis
soa:Parameter.description: Controls Lightspeed GPU-accelerated preanalysis. This can be disabled to improve video quality at low bitrates. This only applies when the 'Lightspeed Accelerated 16-bit YCbCr 4:4:4:4' or 'Cinnafilm Tachyon' VPL is selected.

soa:Parameter.name: Preset (--preset)
soa:Parameter.description: Encoding times for different presets can differ 10x or more times

soa:Parameter.name: Max Number of Reference Frames (--ref)
soa:Parameter.description: Max Reference Frames

soa:Parameter.name: Max Number of B-Frames (--bframes)
soa:Parameter.description: Max Number of Consecutive B-Frames

soa:Codec.name: AAC
soa:Codec.description: Advanced Audio Coding (AAC) is part of the MPEG-4 standard and generally achieves better sound quality than MP3 at similar bitrates. AAC-LC is standardized within ISO/IEC 14496-3 and ISO/IEC 13818-7.

soa:Parameter.description: The audio bit rate, measured in bits per second.

soa:Parameter.name: Audio Tracks
soa:Parameter.description: Number of audio tracks.

soa:Parameter.name: Sample Rate
soa:Parameter.description: The audio sample frequency in Hz (samples/second).

soa:Parameter.name: Bits per Sample

soa:Processor.description: The legacy Telestream video processing library is RGB-based. It offers automated gamut correction and allows advanced overlays such as GraphicsFactory and Screen open subtitling. However, the original library is single-threaded, has fewer options for standards conversion, and requires configuration to ensure color space preservation.
soa:Processor.name: Legacy 8-bit RGB 4:4:4

soa:Processor.description: The multi-core CPU-based processing library operates in full 16-bit 4:4:4:4 YCbCr color space. It can be configured to use multiple CPU cores, and it offers more advanced algorithms for de-interlacing and resizing than the legacy processing library.
soa:Processor.name: Multi-core 16-bit YCbCr 4:4:4:4

soa:Processor.description: The Lightspeed Accelerated processing library requires a Lightspeed Server. It uses GPU acceleration to significantly increase transcoding performance; it also offers more advanced algorithms for de-interlacing and resizing than the legacy processing library.
soa:Processor.name: Lightspeed Accelerated 16-bit YCbCr 4:4:4:4

soa:Processor.description: Cinnafilm Tachyon offers GPU accelerated high-quality video processing with excellent inverse telecine and standards conversion capability.
soa:Processor.name: Cinnafilm Tachyon
